{"id":314812,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-长沙四村民去市政府递交举报材料被逐出/","date":"2013-09-23T09:48:56Z","modified":"2013-09-23T09:48:56Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙四村民去市政府递交举报材料被逐出（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）2013年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>上午，长沙开福区兴联村李香等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>位村民，为联名举报兴联村党支部书记违法搭建房屋，向长沙市委办公厅、市委书记易炼红递交联名举报材料。市委书记易炼红不在，四人递交给办公厅办公室一位姓欧阳的男工作人员，他收了举报材料说：“一定转交易炼红书记。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>李香等四人从市委办公厅下来再去长沙市政府办公厅向市长张剑飞递交联名举报材料，竟然被保安和未穿工作服的男子限制人身自由，不准四人上楼，后强行把四人从市政府拖出，举报材料未能递交。</span></div>\n<div><span></span> </div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-URsqAi_6VZc/UkAEzmbUUkI/AAAAAAAAohQ/LuJOzTa7nRo/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-URsqAi_6VZc/UkAEzmbUUkI/AAAAAAAAohQ/LuJOzTa7nRo/s320/1.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-iYt5emgL_B8/UkAE0JYIMtI/AAAAAAAAohY/k1EMXQxJwf0/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-iYt5emgL_B8/UkAE0JYIMtI/AAAAAAAAohY/k1EMXQxJwf0/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"267\" /></a></div>\n<div><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>  </div>\n<p><span> </span></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[182